Which environment variable can be used to change the default path for a new git repositorycreated with git init?
A)  GIT_DIR
B)  GIT_HOME
C)  GIT_DEST
D)  GIT_LOC
A
A. The GIT_DIR environment variable can be used to change the default location awayfrom the ./.git directory in which a new repository would normally be created. Theother options are not used by git as environment variables.
